{
  "local_port": 36866,
  "remote_port": 443,
  "prompt": "What are some beautiful shayaris for welcoming freshers in college?",
  "response": "Certainly! Here are some beautiful and warm **shayaris** that you can use to welcome freshers in college. These shayaris encapsulate the spirit of new beginnings, friendship, and the excitement of college life:\n\n---\n\n1. **\"Khushbu-e-dosti se mehka karo,  \n   Har pal ko mayyar-e-mastana karo,  \n   Yeh college ka rang hai aur tum ho naya savera,  \n   Is safar ko khubsurat banana karo.\"**  \n   *(Make every moment fragrant with the essence of friendship,  \n   Turn every second into a celebration,  \n   This is the color of college, and you are the new dawn,  \n   Make this journey beautiful.)*\n\n---\n\n2. **\"Naye rishton ki yeh duniya hai,  \n   Naye khwabon ki yeh manzil hai,  \n   Freshers ho tum, aur hum hai saath mein,  \n   Yeh safar hoga yaadgaar, bas muskurao hazar baar.\"**  \n   *(This is a world of new relationships,  \n   This is the destination of new dreams,  \n   You are the freshers, and we are with you,  \n   This journey will be unforgettable, just smile a thousand times.)*\n\n---\n\n3. **\"Jaise phool khilte hain baharon mein,  \n   Waise khiloge tum iss saalon mein,  \n   College ki raunak ho tum,  \n   Yeh safar hoga yaadgaar tumhare liye.\"**  \n   *(Just like flowers bloom in the spring,  \n   You will bloom in these years,  \n   You are the beauty of this college,  \n   This journey will be memorable for you.)*\n\n---\n\n4. **\"Naye saal, naye sapne, naye rishte,  \n   Yeh college ki duniya hai rangin aur resham se bhi jyada sajaavat se bhari,  \n   Freshers ho tum, aur hum hai saath mein,  \n   Apni muskurahaton se yeh rang aur chandni bhar do.\"**  \n   *(New year, new dreams, new relationships,  \n   This world of college is colorful and adorned with more than silk and jewels,  \n   You are the freshers, and we are with you,  \n   Fill this color and moonlight with your smiles.)*\n\n---\n\n5. **\"Chandni raat ko sajane aaye ho,  \n   College mein rang bharne aaye ho,  \n   Har mushkil ko hassenge saath milkar,  \n   Yeh safar hoga yaadgaar tumhare liye.\"**  \n   *(You have come to adorn the moonlit night,  \n   You have come to fill this college with colors,  \n   We will face every challenge together with a smile,  \n   This journey will be unforgettable for you.)*\n\n---\n\n6. **\"Naye chand ki roshni ho tum,  \n   Naye safar ka irshad ho tum,  \n   College ki duniya mein tum ho naya savera,  \n   Aao, milkar isse rangin banaen.\"**  \n   *(You are the light of the new moon,  \n   You are the announcement of a new journey,  \n   In the world of college, you are the new dawn,  \n   Come, let\u2019s make it colorful together.)*\n\n---\n\nThese shayaris are warm, welcoming, and perfect for setting a positive and encouraging tone for the freshers as they embark on their college journey. You can recite them during welcome events, orientation programs, or even share them in greeting cards or posters. \ud83c\udf1f",
  "temperature": 1.0,
